    dc:title "Further studies on south eastern Asian Luciolinae: 1. Sclerotia Ballantyne, a new genus of fireflies with back swimming larvae 2. Triangulara Pimpasalee, a new genus from Thailand (Coleoptera: Lampyridae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258001>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.257998>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.257996>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258004>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258005>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258006>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.257999>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258000>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258007> ;
