<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258001>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 − 28. Sclerotia gen. nov. spp. males. 17, 18 Scl. aquatilis. 19, 20 Luciola cingulata type male (MCSN). 21, 22 Luciola brahmina type male (MNHN). 23, 24 Luciola seriata holotype male (MCSN). 25, 26 Scl. carinata male (SAMA). 27, 28 Scl. fui sp. nov. paratype males (NHMHAU). 17, 19, 21, 23, 25, 27, 28 dorsal; 18, 20, 22, 24, 26 ventral. Specimens are not to scale and are assembled to allow comparison of elytral and abdominal features." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258001/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.257998>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Neighbour Joining bootstrap consensus tree of several aquatic fireflies in South East Asia, with firefly Pyrocoelia pectoralis as outgroup." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/257998/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.257996>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. The first of two sections of the Majority rule tree, consensus of 562 MPT of length 5687 from phylogenetic analysis of 145 taxa and 438 morphological characters in Ballantyne et al. (2015, Fig. 1 A) showing Sclerotia Ballantyne gen. nov. and Triangulara Pimpasalee gen. nov. and % of MPTs with the node. For those nodes found in 100 % of MPT, the % is shown in bold." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/257996/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258004>
    dc:description "FIGURES 39 − 44. Scl. aquatilis males and female (41). 39, 40 Thailand (ANIC); 42 − 44 India (ANIC). 39, 42, 53 dorsal; 40, 41, 44 ventral. Scale lines are 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258004/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258005>
    dc:description "FIGURES 45 − 46. Scl. aquatilis aedeagal sheath and aedeagus (posterior half only), sclerites and tergite 8. 45 dorsal; 46 ventral. Scale lines are 1 mm. Figure legend: 1 right sclerite; 2 left sclerite; 3 ventral sclerite; 4 left arm tergite 8; 5 posterior area aedeagal sheath in area of emargination; 6 ML aedeagus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258005/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258006>
    dc:description "FIGURES 47 − 55. Luciolinae males Table 4. 47, 48 Luciola clara possible type (MNHN). 49, 50 Luciola curticollis syntype male (MNHN). 51, 55 Luciola noctivaga possible type (MNHN). 47, 49, 51 dorsal (49 elytra only); 48, 50 ventral (50 abdomen and elytra only); 52 − 55 specimen labels. Scale line is 1 mm. Not all figures are to scale, dimensions are quoted in text." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258006/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.257999>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4 − 12. Luciolinae Table 3. 4 − 6 Luciola ambita male (MNHN). 7 − 9 Luciola delauneyi male (MNHN). 10 − 12 Luciola flebilis female (MNHN). 4, 7, 10 specimen label; 5, 9, ventral (9 abdomen only); 6, 8, 11 dorsal (6 anterior body only; 8 elytra only); 12 right lateral. Scale line is 1 mm. Figs 6, 8, 9, 11, 12 are not to scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/257999/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258000>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 − 16. Luciolinae Table 3. Luciola semimarginata syntype male (MNHN). 13 specimen label; 14 dorsal; 15 ventral; 16 ventral detail terminal abdominal ventrites. Scale line is 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258000/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258007>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56 − 62. Luciolinae males Table 4. 56 − 59, 62 Luciola timida (MNHN). 60, 61, 62 Luciola tenuicornis (MNHN). 56, 59, 60, 62 dorsal (59 terminal abdomen only, left posterior arm of tergite 8 arrowed); 57, 58 ventral (58 terminal abdomen only); 61 specimen labels. Scale lines are 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258007/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

